Author: 237randomnumber
Text: All of this happened within a span of 2 years. It's due to overeating.

Author: Braseford
Text: How old were you when you developed your ED? I’m constantly yearning to the weight I was when I was 17. But that’s the thing - a lot of us are skinnier when we are teenagers because that’s how bodies work. I hated that I got bigger hips and boobs and the weight gain that comes with it. But I’m having to accept that that wasn’t due to overeating, but due to growing up and maturing.   There is no way to tell if you’d have otherwise stayed with a BMI of 20
